# License — vendor/libav-hevc

This directory contains pre-built WebAssembly binaries of the libav.js
"hevc-aac" variant. The binaries are compiled from the following sources:

## Components and Licenses

### FFmpeg (libavformat, libavcodec, libavutil, libswresample, libswscale)
- Version: 8.0
- License: **GNU Lesser General Public License v2.1 or later (LGPL-2.1+)**
- Copyright: (c) 2000-2024 Fabrice Bellard et al
- Source: `node_modules/libav.js/sources/ffmpeg-8.0.tar.xz`

### Emscripten C runtime (musl libc)
- License: **MIT / ISC**
- Copyright: (c) 2010-2024 Emscripten authors; (c) 2005-2024 Rich Felker et al
- Source: bundled with Emscripten SDK

### libav.js wrapper
- Version: 6.8.8
- License: **0-Clause BSD (0BSD)** — no attribution required in derivatives
- Copyright: (c) Yahweasel and contributors
- Source: `node_modules/libav.js/sources/libav.js.tar.xz`

## LGPL Compliance

The LGPL-2.1 requires that source code be made available to recipients of the
binary. Sources for all LGPL-licensed components are included in the libav.js
npm package at `node_modules/libav.js/sources/`. Build instructions are in
`scripts/build-wasm.mjs`.

The full text of the LGPL-2.1 is available at:
https://www.gnu.org/licenses/old-licenses/lgpl-2.1.html
